# Questions

<!-- This file tracks questions raised during due diligence.
     Each question is an H2 heading with the question ID, followed by a
     fenced YAML code block with metadata.

     Format:

     ## Q-001
     ```yaml
     question: "Why did revenue drop 15% in Q3?"
     workstream: financial
     owner: self
     status: open
     date_raised: "2026-04-07"
     context:
       key: annual_revenue
       old_value: "2400000"
       new_value: "2040000"
     ```

     Questions can be raised manually or generated automatically when
     the verification gate rejects a fact update (discrepancy context
     is stored in the context field).

     Valid owners: self, principal, seller, broker, counsel.
     Valid statuses: open, answered, deferred.

     This file is managed by diligent commands. Manual edits are
     supported but must preserve the H2 + fenced YAML structure. -->
